{"tid":266564,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[東京遊記] 五月尾東京6日6夜隨心玩樂之旅","createTime":"2017-06-01T14:34:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-03T07:55:51.000Z","uid":80035,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b0e603163b17a31dbb43ed0db79fa8353c4ac57c","tid":266564,"uid":80035,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T14:34:50.000Z","msg":"[少圖] 五月尾東京6日6夜隨心玩樂之旅<br />\n第一次寫遊記，成程掛住食同玩冇乜影到相<br />\n因為發覺好易唔記得個trip做左啲乜，所以想record低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n臨時臨急搵左個fd去東京乜野都冇plan過，淨係係咁易諗過下有咩想做<br />\n連yen都係去到果邊7仔先撳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n5月24 DAY 1 香港機場－＞成田空港<br />\n原本下午1點機，6點到成田，頂你黑雨仲要有班大陸機衝出跑道，搞到無限delay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n結果9點先到機場，媽的仲約左airbnb個host 9點係新宿等<br />\n入左境第一時間搞sim卡，而家成田機場有得免費拎sim卡，慳返唔少，仲要打到電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/wamazing-sim-card-to-tw-and-hk-visitor_00.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F01%2Fwamazing-sim-card-to-tw-and-hk-visitor_00.png&h=038746fa&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n搞掂就買飛坐NEX去新宿，成功check in已經11點半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今次搵airbnb比較遲，淨係搵到三丁目果頭，行去JR新宿要成2／3個字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/1TqfqKY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F1TqfqKY.jpg&h=6465b27e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n放低行李就仆左落街搵野食，去左食鳥貴族，尼間野其實周圍都有<br />\n所有野均一價280yen唔洗，又開到深夜，岩晒夜鬼（張圖求其上網搵）<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/3gSXBoq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F3gSXBoq.jpg&h=c7e44138&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最後當然唔少得便利店，次次去到都狂食森永隻牛奶布丁，連稅先100yen<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/inpb4rj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Finpb4rj.jpg&h=972e3dc2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n返到宿就plan行程 plan撚到3點半果陣&hellip;竟然天光，O撚晒"},{"pid":"c22cde0c177e691101f86d0d3decaa2958bed7ca","tid":266564,"uid":41614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T14:35:49.000Z","msg":"lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88489d756048c27ea3bcaa68a646b88720d87462","tid":266564,"uid":70593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T14:42:56.000Z","msg":"lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b042dc638a5ab028135a4a3e4f0e704030fde7a","tid":266564,"uid":80035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T15:26:46.000Z","msg":"DAY2 新宿－＞銀座<br />\n琴晚plan到天光都淨係plan左要去富士急玩同去河口湖既芝櫻祭<br />\n交通手段乜春都冇諗過，仲要搞到今日遲左起身，所以今日都係行下街食下野算<br />\n友人話想食壽司，就去左食美登利，一search發現原來新宿店裝修<br />\n咁就買左張metro pass 900yen 搭地下鐵仆去銀座果間排隊<br />\n去到11點人山人海，拎左張飛，就係銀座行下行下行左去有樂町<br />\n有樂町站附近有間LOFT搬遷做緊大減價，有d仲賣到3折（新假期有時d料其實都唔差）<br />\n行到咁上下返返去美登利就有得入去，想食鮟鱇魚肝所以叫左個ひだまり<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/r6fWd7b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fr6fWd7b.jpg&h=a9c1aaa8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第二次食，不過不失啦&hellip;下次應該會試下おまかせ<br />\n好似好多高級店都要神咁早book定，有冇巴絲打比較熟<br />\n食完lunch走左去GINZA SIX尼個新開既mall，樓上有咩賣我就唔知<br />\n淨係知地下有好多甜品舖，真係食到糖尿都似<br />\n最後同班師奶闊太少女OL一齊排隊買布丁，成800幾yen一個<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/pfNxtEr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FpfNxtEr.jpg&h=cf3cd4f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/xfG4S23.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FxfG4S23.jpg&h=61ea0fba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最後個布丁排撚左半個幾鐘，on9完之後友人話要買op figure俾屋企人，所以去左老秋<br />\n<br />\n銀座－＞秋葉原<br />\n好多kawaii既女僕派傳單仲有好多鬼佬周街影相，都唔知影乜鳩<br />\n紅極一時既k-on，而家只需600yen就買到<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/heQgZEi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FheQgZEi.jpg&h=14dac6f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最後仲係幢綠色既buliding到買左好多隻杯，之後路過AKB CAFE入去飲左杯野<br />\n<br />\n秋葉原－＞涉谷<br />\n夜晚去左涉谷諗住行下新開既mega驚安，但沿途太多靚女，耽誤晒行程<br />\n所以都係醫左肚先，google左間叫うえの既燒肉，去到先知唔book位食唔到<br />\n求鳩求入左間餐廳叫左個漢堡餐，2000yen，估唔到有驚喜，塊扒肉汁多到係咁必出黎<br />\n食完野去到驚安揀左啲野見到條退稅隊長到&hellip;都係放返低去車站趕終電"},{"pid":"209f61dcb378e105bee692758e55e348a3b9c9b0","tid":266564,"uid":80035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T16:03:38.000Z","msg":"DAY3 新宿－＞熱海<br />\n本來plan好今日去富士急，聽日去河口湖，神咁早5點起身諗住book巴士套票<br />\n一起身睇天氣，仆街落雨，可以訓返，8點起身決定即興去熱海浸溫泉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係新宿JR買左張JR PASS就出發，個幾鐘左右就到左熱海<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/TiPLyQI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FTiPLyQI.jpg&h=9d6b279f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n真不愧為東京人既度假天堂，沿途一個遊客都冇，難得既清靜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n金目鯛好似幾出名，間間和食店都推介<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/KJ9wu32.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FKJ9wu32.jpg&h=84dad695&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n味道唔錯，不過條魚煮得老左少少<br />\n食飽飯就去左information center搵leaflet睇邊度有日帰り温泉<br />\n最後搭巴士去左間個景唔錯既秀花園 湯の花膳<br />\n可能因為閒日，成間野乜人都冇，包晒場咁慢慢浸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n溫泉到望到既景，夜晚應該靚到不得了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/cQt05ev.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FcQt05ev.jpg&h=4ab3e03b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n斷斷續續浸左成粒鐘先捨得走，返轉頭搵唔到巴士站所以行路<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/2l2OsjB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F2l2OsjB.jpg&h=4ffc1615&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/IunbQxv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FIunbQxv.jpg&h=6559034f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n幾鐘意尼種hea下hea下周圍又冇乜人既feel，係車站行左陣商店街就返涉谷<br />\n<br />\n熱海－＞涉谷<br />\n繼續琴日既驚安之旅，由於買既野唔多，最後連稅都懶得退食dinner算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n出到黎又唔知食乜好，見到天下一品，醒起佢係年輕男性最鐘意既連鎖拉麵店第一名（by濕鳩ranking網）<br />\n入到去叫左個set，1000yen樓下有拉麵，餃子，炒飯都幾抵食，不過個炒飯就&hellip;<br />\n不過重點都係有個好靚既女店員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n返到新宿經過花園神社，原來尼日開始連續都係祭典<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好多人好熱鬧好有氣氛，可惜啲相影晒係snapchat<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見到抽獎有ps4，咁就掉左幾百yen落海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f979e81650b87a2f2c1a5141420a5359ea9facfb","tid":266564,"uid":80035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T17:03:50.000Z","msg":"DAY4 新宿－＞富士急<br />\n用JR PASS係新宿坐到去大月再轉富士急行線<br />\n7點出門口，9點半左右到左富士急<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/VaujvQO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FVaujvQO.jpg&h=ffd98b29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n星期六人唔算多，勁好天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/owfa4ll.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fowfa4ll.jpg&h=84d4643f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/f7V9ZaB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Ff7V9ZaB.jpg&h=93c6a341&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n全日玩左5個機動遊戲加鬼屋，鬼屋真心唔差，佈景做得好好<br />\n明知個位有人會出黎嚇你，但如果夠投入enjoy既話其實真係可以好刺激<br />\n一有人彈出黎我同個fd即刻係咁跑好似走佬咁，好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nええじゃないか，痂撚線，成個場最撚激應該係尼部<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nFUJIYAMA，好長好快既升級版越礦飛車，第二激<br />\n高飛車，排最耐係佢，未玩之前最滿淆又係佢，turn out最輕鬆果部<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n鉄骨番長，玩完頭暈<br />\n跳樓機同op果部差唔多，同條日本妹一齊坐<br />\n上到頂勁淆一齊傻笑鳩叫，走果陣仲同我揮手byebye<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n後悔趕JR走冇問到佢拎line<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/AVqcySv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FAVqcySv.jpg&h=bb98c855&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n富士急－＞新宿<br />\n返新宿食晚飯，上網google左間叫土古里好似都唔差就去左<br />\n好彩唔洗book位都入到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/yiPMYGW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FyiPMYGW.jpg&h=dfcdebee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/ufjdkKr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FufjdkKr.jpg&h=ea230de2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n叫左個6800幾yen既放題course<br />\n其實食咁肥既肉好易食到膩，下次都係單點啲高級啲既肉算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/AtWtSyv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FAtWtSyv.jpg&h=57db029f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n高橋みなみ<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n食完燒肉去family mart買香口膠<br />\n有欅坂file送，拎左個平手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b9e21b2cd45f4343f82291696ba25fec0cd6794","tid":266564,"uid":80035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T17:28:00.000Z","msg":"DAY5 新宿－＞原宿<br />\n本來諗住用埋張JR PASS去埋輕井澤，點知琴晚飲左酒一訓訓撚到11點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n落街撞正花園神社例大祭既遊行<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Es9NF1O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FEs9NF1O.jpg&h=06ed84b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n到左原宿，表參道同竹下通多人到仆街<br />\n行完一轉就走左，經過間滑板店，買左舊用滑板整既鎖匙扣<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/1MqgbbN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F1MqgbbN.jpg&h=02ccf7ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係原宿搵左勁耐都唔係好搵到野食，最後食左間中華料理店既放題2000幾yen<br />\n雖然係日式中國菜，但又幾好味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n食完野都4點，去左明治神宮<br />\n可惜修輯緊，個神宮變左幅畫，連相都廢事影了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n夜晚諗唔到食乜食左CoCo壱番屋算鳩數<br />\n之後去宿附近既棒球中心打棒球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n極頹既一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"576c8618c27197d14c0d94d3c83458c098077279","tid":266564,"uid":80035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T17:58:20.000Z","msg":"DAY6 新宿－＞巢鴨－＞品川<br />\nlasy day晨咁早起身去排隊食米芝連1星拉麵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n7點半去到巢鴨站，入到舖擺低1000yen訂金，拎張11點既整理卷就走左<br />\n係附近既coffee shop食個早餐hea下hea下都係9點，仲有2粒鐘都唔知點hea<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n附近乜駕都未開完全冇野行，連卡拉OK都未開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後去左便利店企係到睇下雜誌，睇睇下就11點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n11點返到去已經開始打緊蛇餅，11點半先入到舖<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Y6PPZPn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FY6PPZPn.jpg&h=e0252453&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/He9GNmz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FHe9GNmz.jpg&h=94241ce1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n搞左咁撚耐就係為碗麵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n湯底由幾種醬油溝成，個味幾深奧，撈埋黑松露醬更加香<br />\n麵質感特別，第一次食到尼種口感，筍乾好大條，但係完全冇渣<br />\n平衡度高同清新，唔會好易食膩<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/r3LcL6G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fr3LcL6G.jpg&h=243c29e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新出既無色檸檬茶<br />\n<br />\n巢鴨－＞品川<br />\n食完拉麵去品川既水族館<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/cAG06rW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FcAG06rW.jpg&h=8b495466&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n途中見到幾個妹妹仔係到採花，勁寫意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/LM6Z9wf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FLM6Z9wf.jpg&h=756c6fb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n睇下唔同既魚仔～<br />\n<br />\n品川－＞新宿<br />\n夜晚返返新宿拎gip（其實放左個gip係新宿蠢左）<br />\n食埋一直都好想試既文字燒，點知整都成pat野咁<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/9OzVGgp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F9OzVGgp.jpg&h=ba1ba096&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n都係お好み焼き易整啲，又好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己俾錢要自己燒埋仲要成身煙味，真係體驗過就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/ko3vTjn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fko3vTjn.jpg&h=b0b11840&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最後係書店買左本白麻bb寫真就起程去羽田喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7225ede864ebf4bc804b4ad92c00f5a0ccecdddc","tid":266564,"uid":31629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T18:06:18.000Z","msg":"會唔會係開登以來最快搞掂既遊記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72e36d38f99d2abf6e51e4793799cd406bb81936","tid":266564,"uid":16133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T21:03:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會唔會係開登以來最快搞掂既遊記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好有效率<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eae14a8b168a0