17-06-03T07:16:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主有冇去埋河口湖玩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇 落大雨冇去到，轉左去熱海hea<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n留返下次爬富士山一次過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2730de40934adf2b49f6a24ac682c7d7e069f833","tid":266564,"uid":60151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T07:27:28.000Z","msg":"後日會去河口湖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ece7190587b11bf76039542fc6cbd8c352b5f43","tid":266564,"uid":94189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T07:55:51.000Z","msg":"同巴打同一日出發不過去台中 <br />\n等咗3個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}